fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/59493/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/100560/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-08-25/201908251566725301.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">7.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/100560/">长安诡事之末世神兵</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%AD%99%E8%AE%AF------------/" target="_blank">孙讯</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%9F%B3%E9%9B%AA%E5%A9%A7------------/" target="_blank">石雪婧</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%9A%93%E4%B9%94------------/" target="_blank">皓乔</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%90%B4%E6%89%BF%E5%B3%B0--------/" target="_blank">吴承峰</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2019/" target="_blank">2019</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.27</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>星罗城的本国与扶余发生战争，辛礼与副将马一成带一支精锐偷袭扶余大营失败，被迫向东转进，途中遭遇神兵不死军的袭击，幸得少女灵儿相助，灵儿熟知神兵特性，帮助众人成功逃到星罗城，众人以为逃出生天之际，却发现又陷入了另一个更大的危机&nbsp;</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/100560/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/95847/" data-original="https://img.1977zy.cc/upload/vod/2019-07-31/201907311564563924.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">8.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">更新至02集</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/95847/">男神恋爱系统第一季</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/4/" target="_blank">动漫</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2019/" target="_blank">2019</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.27</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>31岁的林棠蝉联了七届金话筒奖后，在回家途中遭遇车祸身亡，被系统附身来到另外一个世界，成为风华视频的新主持人系统让女主攻略四位男神，分别是风华视频的总裁叶凌恒、游泳冠军苏穆、当红偶像顾星辰、钢琴天才陆离。只有成功攻略四位男神，女主才能重生返回原来的世界。林棠初来乍到，叶凌恒便通知她节目即将取缔。林棠</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/95847/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/58222/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-01-30/154882437418.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">6.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">BD高清</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/58222/">医神</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%BC%A0%E8%BE%BE%E6%98%8E------------/" target="_blank">张达明</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%94%A1%E5%B0%91%E8%8A%AC------------/" target="_blank">蔡少芬</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%BC%8D%E5%92%8F%E8%96%87------------/" target="_blank">伍咏薇</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BB%8E%E8%80%80%E7%A5%A5------------/" target="_blank">黎耀祥</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E8%BE%89--------/" target="_blank">刘国辉</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1999/" target="_blank">1999</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.27</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>田七（张达明 饰）是个精人，常喝醉打妻子当归（蔡少芬 饰），当归痛定思痛发誓要对夫报复，刚巧城中富商罗汉果欲寻名医，当归于是谎称丈夫会医术，并且要用精棍子揍田七，他才会应允他人治医，罗汉果信以为真，不但将田七痛打一顿，并将其接入家中，于是一场啼笑皆非的闹剧开始了……</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/58222/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/99861/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-08-24/201908241566641437.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">3.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/99861/">武神黑侠</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%A8%8A%E5%B0%91%E7%9A%87------------/" target="_blank">樊少皇</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%83%91%E4%BD%A9%E4%BD%A9------------/" target="_blank">郑佩佩</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%B0%AD%E7%AD%A0%E6%80%A1------------/" target="_blank">谭筠怡</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%9E%97%E4%BF%8A%E6%9D%B0--------/" target="_blank">林俊杰</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/6/" target="_blank">动作片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2001/" target="_blank">2001</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.27</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>傅天明是电脑奇才，他的姑姐?安娜是他的私人秘书每当「赤神帮」犯罪时?天明便会变成黑侠对付他们。 一次行动中，「赤神帮」在监狱中救了首领赤神，更偷走了「依波拉」病毒。天明和安娜为了追查此时而认识了少琪，她发现可对抗依波拉病毒的抗体，令赤神要把她捉到手上。原来赤神偷了病毒是有项重大的阴谋，黑侠为了阻止赤</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/99861/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/99695/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-08-23/201908231566548440.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">2.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/99695/">神探磨辘</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%88%98%E9%9D%92%E4%BA%91------------/" target="_blank">刘青云</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%92%9F%E4%B8%BD%E7%BC%87------------/" target="_blank">钟丽缇</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%BC%8D%E5%92%8F%E8%96%87------------/" target="_blank">伍咏薇</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%90%B4%E9%95%87%E5%AE%87------------/" target="_blank">吴镇宇</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%86%AF%E7%B4%A0%E6%B3%A2------------/" target="_blank">冯素波</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%8F%B6%E7%AB%9E%E7%94%9F------------/" target="_blank">叶竞生</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%BC%A0%E5%BF%97%E6%88%90--------/" target="_blank">张志成</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/8/" target="_blank">爱情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1994/" target="_blank">1994</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.27</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>陆志摩服务警界十年，办事鲁莽，每次都由女上司黄雪笙化险为夷，其后他发现黄鲜为人知的同性恋秘密，但他不仅为她紧守秘密，甚至成为她的爱情军师这对工作上的冤家拍挡，竟同时发展为感情知己……&nbsp;</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/99695/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><div class="fed-page-info fed-text-center"><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-hide fed-show-xs-inline" href="/s/%E7%A5%9E------------/">首页</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info" href="/s/%E7%A5%9E----------3---/">上页</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-hide fed-show-sm-inline" href="/s/%E7%A5%9E------------/">1</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-hide fed-show-sm-inline fed-btns-disad" href="javascript:;">...</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-hide fed-show-sm-inline" href="/s/%E7%A5%9E----------3---/">3</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-hide fed-show-sm-inline fed-btns-green" href="javascript:;">4</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-hide fed-show-sm-inline" href="/s/%E7%A5%9E----